snippet.title: GoPro: Amber the Downhill Dog
snippet.description:
Follow the adventures of James Roxburgh and his adorable dog, Amber, through the woods of Aldershot, England for an unforgettable ride. 

See more of Amber at https://www.youtube.com/user/norcorider2005

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera from ‪http://GoPro.com.

Get stoked and subscribe: http://goo.gl/HgVXpQ

Music
Twin Shadow "At My Heels"
